Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
We check what are possible moments \[Gamma]1 for positive semidefiniteness of \
the Hankel matrix. It turns out that there is only one choice due to 0 being \
in the support of the measure for the original sequence.\
\>", "Section",
